state.text:
Change the texture with the Texture patch – click the pencil to load a new texture.

Adjust repeat with the patches.

To use a color rather  than a texture, connect the color picker to the color slot on the Material patch

You can adjust the Ground plane settings here. Unlock the object to move it with the Lock switch.

Open the Repeating Surface patch to change the texture or adjust its tiling
Adjust the resolution of the sphere by increasing or decreasing the number of segments with the Segments patch

You can change the texture of the ball with the texture loader at top left.

And add color with the color picker at left. The Phong material patch gives (many) options for setting the material properties .

Connect the Sky texture
into the texture slot
if you want a texture instead of color for your sky. 

Use the Fog near & Far 
to adjust the distance
 fog effect
